<tr>
<th class="summary" colspan="2" style="background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;">Vietnam War</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;">Part of the <a href="/wiki/Cold_War" title="Cold War">Cold War</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="text-align: center; font-size: 90%; border-bottom: 1px solid #aaa; line-height: 1.5em;"><a href="/wiki/File:UH-1combatmission1970.jpg" class="image" title="UH-1combatmission1970.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d5/UH-1combatmission1970.jpg/300px-UH-1combatmission1970.jpg" width="300" height="239" border="0" /></a><br />
A South Vietnamese Air Force <a href="/wiki/UH-1_Iroquois" title="UH-1 Iroquois">UH-1</a> helicopter over the <a href="/wiki/Mekong_Delta" title="Mekong Delta">Mekong Delta</a> in 1970</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2">
<table class="infobox" width="100%" style="margin: 0; cellpadding: 0; padding: 0; border: 0;">
<tr>
<th style="padding-right: 1em;">Date</th>
<td>1959<sup id="cite_ref-WarBegan_0-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-WarBegan-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup> – April 30, 1975</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="padding-right: 1em;">Location</th>
<td><span class="location"><a href="/wiki/Vietnam" title="Vietnam">Vietnam</a>, <a href="/wiki/Cambodia" title="Cambodia">Cambodia</a>, and <a href="/wiki/Laos" title="Laos">Laos</a></span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="padding-right: 1em;">Result</th>
<td>North Vietnamese Victory
<ul>
<li>Communist takeover of South Vietnam, Cambodia and Laos.</li>
</ul>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="padding-right: 1em;">Territorial<br />
changes</th>
<td>Unification of North and South Vietnam</td>
</tr>
</table>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
