<td width="50%" style="border-right: 1px dotted #aaa;"><span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/South_Vietnam" title="South Vietnam"><img alt="Flag of South Vietnam" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e9/Flag_of_South_Vietnam.svg/22px-Flag_of_South_Vietnam.svg.png" width="22" height="15" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a></span> <b>South Vietnam</b> 220,357 dead;<sup id="cite_ref-aaron_5-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-aaron-5" title=""><span>[</span>6<span>]</span></a></sup> 1,170,000 wounded<br />
<span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/United_States" title="United States"><img alt="Flag of the United States" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a4/Flag_of_the_United_States.svg/22px-Flag_of_the_United_States.svg.png" width="22" height="12" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a></span> <b>US</b> 58,159 dead;<sup id="cite_ref-aaron_5-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-aaron-5" title=""><span>[</span>6<span>]</span></a></sup> 2,000 missing; 303,635 wounded<sup id="cite_ref-6" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-6" title=""><span>[</span>7<span>]</span></a></sup><br />
<span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/South_Korea" title="South Korea"><img alt="Flag of South Korea" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/09/Flag_of_South_Korea.svg/22px-Flag_of_South_Korea.svg.png" width="22" height="15" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a></span> <b>South Korea</b> 4,960 dead; 10,962 wounded<br />
<span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Thailand" title="Thailand"><img alt="Flag of Thailand" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a9/Flag_of_Thailand.svg/22px-Flag_of_Thailand.svg.png" width="22" height="15" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a></span> <b>Thailand</b> 1,351 dead<sup id="cite_ref-aaron_5-2" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-aaron-5" title=""><span>[</span>6<span>]</span></a></sup><br />
<span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Australia" title="Australia"><img alt="Flag of Australia" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b9/Flag_of_Australia.svg/22px-Flag_of_Australia.svg.png" width="22" height="11" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a></span> <b>Australia</b> 520 dead;<sup id="cite_ref-aaron_5-3" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-aaron-5" title=""><span>[</span>6<span>]</span></a></sup> 2,400* wounded<br />
<span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/New_Zealand" title="New Zealand"><img alt="Flag of New Zealand" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3e/Flag_of_New_Zealand.svg/22px-Flag_of_New_Zealand.svg.png" width="22" height="11" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a></span> <b>New Zealand</b> 37 dead; 187 wounded
<p><b>Total dead: 285,831<br /></b>Total wounded: ~1,490,000</p>
</td>
