n_Wahiawa&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Operation Wahiawa (page does not exist)">Wahiawa</a></i> – <i><a href="/wiki/Operation_Hastings" title="Operation Hastings">Hastings</a></i> – <a href="/w/index.php?title=Battle_on_Minh_Thanh_Road&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Battle on Minh Thanh Road (page does not exist)">Minh Thanh Road</a> – <i><a href="/wiki/Operation_Prairie" title="Operation Prairie">Prairie</a></i>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c_C%C6%A1" title="Battle of Đức Cơ">Đức Cơ</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Long_T%E1%BA%A7n" title="Battle of Long Tần">Long Tần</a>&#160;– <i><a href="/wiki/Operation_Beaver_Cage" title="Operation Beaver Cage">Beaver Cage</a></i>&#160;– <i><a href="/wiki/Operation_Attleboro" title="Operation Attleboro">Attleboro</a></i>&#160;– <a href="/w/index.php?title=Viet_Cong_attack_on_Tan_Son_Nhut_airbase&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Viet Cong attack on Tan Son Nhut airbase (page does not exist)">Tân Sơn Nhứt</a>&#160;– <a href="/w/index.php?title=Battle_of_LZ_Bird&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Battle of LZ Bird (page does not exist)">LZ Bird</a>&#160;– <i><a href="/wiki/Operation_Deckhouse_Five" title="Operation Deckhouse Five">Deckhouse Five</a></i>&#160;– <i><a href="/wiki/Operation_Cedar_Falls" title="Operation Cedar Falls">Cedar Falls</a></i>&#160;– <i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Operation_Tuscaloosa&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Operation Tuscaloosa (page does not exist)">Tuscaloosa</a></i>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Tra_Binh_Dong" title="Battle of Tra Binh Dong">Tra Binh Dong</a>&#160;– <i><a href="/wiki/Operation_Bribie" title="Operation Bribie">Bribie</a></i>&#160;– <i><a href="/wiki/Operation_Junction_City" title="Operation Junction City">Junction City</a></i> – <i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Operation_Francis_Marion&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Operation Francis Marion (page does not exist)">Francis Marion</a></i> – <i><a href="/wiki/Operation_Union" title="Operation Union">Union</a></i> – <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Hill_881" title="Battle of Hill 881">Hill 881</a> – <a href="/w/index.php?title=Second_Battle_of_Ap_Bac&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Second Battle of Ap Bac (page does not exist)">2nd Ap Bac</a>&#160;– <i><a href="/wiki/Operations_Malheur_I_and_Malheur_II" title="Operations Malheur I and Malheur II">Malheur I and Malheur II</a></i>&#160;– <i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Operation_Baker&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Operation Baker (page does not exist)">Baker</a></i> – <a href="/w/index.php?title=Nine_Days_in_May&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Nine Days in May (page does not exist)">Nine Days in May</a> – <i><a href="/wiki/Operation_Union_II" title="Operation Union II">Union II</a></i> – <a href="/w/index.php?title=Battle_of_Vinh_Huy&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Battle of Vinh Huy (page does not exist)">Vinh Huy</a> – <i><a href="/wiki/Operation_Buffalo_(Vietnam)" title="Operation Buffalo (Vietnam)">Buffalo</a></i> – <a href="/w/index.php?title=Con_Thien_Ambush&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Con Thien Ambush (page does not exist)">Con Thien</a> – <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_July_Two" title="Battle of July Two">July Two</a> – <i><a href="/wiki/Operation_Hong_Kil_Dong" title="Operation Hong Kil Dong">Hong Kil Dong</a></i> – <i><a href="/wiki/Operation_Swift" title="Operation Swift">Swift</a></i> – <a href="/w/index.php?title=Battle_of_Dong_Son&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Battle of Dong Son (page does not exist)">Dong Son</a> – <i><a href="/wiki/Wheeler_wallawa" title="Wheeler wallawa">Wheeler/Wallowa</a></i> – <i><a href="/wiki/Operation_Medina" title="Operation Medina">Medina</a></i>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Ong_Thanh" title="Battle of Ong Thanh">Ông Thanh</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Loc_Ninh_1967" titl