ge does not exist)">Duc Lap</a>&#160;– <i><a href="/wiki/Operation_Sealords" title="Operation Sealords">Sealords</a></i>&#160;– <i><a href="/wiki/Operation_Speedy_Express" title="Operation Speedy Express">Speedy Express</a></i>&#160;– <i><a href="/wiki/Operation_Dewey_Canyon" title="Operation Dewey Canyon">Dewey Canyon</a></i>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Tet_1969" title="Tet 1969">2nd Tet</a>&#160;– <i><a href="/wiki/Operation_Apache_Snow" title="Operation Apache Snow">Apache Snow</a></i>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Hamburger_Hill" title="Battle of Hamburger Hill">Hamburger Hill</a> – <i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Operation_Twinkletoes&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Operation Twinkletoes (page does not exist)">Twinkletoes</a></i> – <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Binh_Ba" title="Battle of Binh Ba">Binh Ba</a>&#160;– <a href="/w/index.php?title=Battle_for_LZ_Kate&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Battle for LZ Kate (page does not exist)">LZ Kate</a>&#160;– <a href="/w/index.php?title=Battle_of_Bu_Prang&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Battle of Bu Prang (page does not exist)">Bu Prang</a>&#160;– <i><a href="/wiki/Operation_Texas_Star" title="Operation Texas Star">Texas Star</a></i>&#160;– <i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Operation_Chicago_Peak&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Operation Chicago Peak (page does not exist)">Chicago Peak</a></i>&#160;– <a href="/w/index.php?title=Battle_at_Khe_Gio_Bridge&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Battle at Khe Gio Bridge (page does not exist)">Khe Gio Bridge</a>&#160;– <i><a href="/wiki/Cambodian_Campaign" title="Cambodian Campaign">Cambodia</a></i>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Kompong_Speu" title="Battle of Kompong Speu">Kompong Speu</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Prey_Veng" title="Battle of Prey Veng">Prey Veng</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Snuol" title="Battle of Snuol">Snuol</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Fire_Support_Base_Ripcord" t