n Triangle">Iron Triangle</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Svay_Rieng" title="Battle of Svay Rieng">Svay Rieng</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Phuoc_Long" title="Battle of Phuoc Long">Phuoc Long</a>&#160;– <i><a href="/wiki/Ho_Chi_Minh_Campaign" title="Ho Chi Minh Campaign">Ho Chi Minh</a></i>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Bu%C3%B4n_Ma_Thu%E1%BB%99t" title="Battle of Buôn Ma Thuột" class="mw-redirect">Buôn Ma Thuột</a>&#160;– <i><a href="/wiki/Operation_New_Life" title="Operation New Life">New Life</a></i>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Xu%C3%A2n_L%E1%BB%99c" title="Battle of Xuân Lộc">Xuân Lộc</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Truong_Sa" title="Battle of Truong Sa">Truong Sa</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Fall_of_Saigon" title="Fall of Saigon">2nd Saigon</a>&#160;– <i><a href="/wiki/Mayag%C3%BCez_incident" title="Mayagüez incident">SS Mayagüez</a></i>
