<li id="cite_note-165"><b><a href="#cite_ref-165" title="">^</a></b> <a href="/wiki/Keith_Payne" title="Keith Payne">Keith Payne</a> was the last Australian to be awarded a <a href="/wiki/Victoria_Cross" title="Victoria Cross">Victoria Cross</a>. In 1991 the <a href="/wiki/Victoria_Cross_for_Australia" title="Victoria Cross for Australia">Victoria Cross for Australia</a> replaced the original Victoria Cross as the highest award for bravery for Australians.</li>
