<li>Summers, Harry G. <a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=MIENAAAACAAJ" class="external text" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=MIENAAAACAAJ" rel="nofollow"><i>On Strategy: The Vietnam War in Context</i></a>, Lightning Source Inc, (2002), <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/1410204197" class="internal">ISBN 1410204197</a> (152 pages)</li>
